OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776625869
OL,3,CThe main pledges from Wales' smaller
OL,4,Cparties ahead of the Senedd Election
OL,6,FWith the Senedd Election less than
OL,7,Fthree weeks away, all of Wales'
OL,8,Fpolitical parties have set out their
OL,9,Fstall and published their manifestos
OL,10,Fto pitch for votes.
OL,12,FThere are six major political parties
OL,13,Fin Wales but there are also several
OL,14,Fsmaller parties.
OL,16,FVoters will head to polling stations
OL,17,Fon 7 May to cast their vote, choosing
OL,18,Fthe party or independent candidate
OL,19,Fthey want to represent their area in
OL,20,Fthe Senedd.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/13
