OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776625869
OL,3,CThe main pledges from Wales' smaller
OL,4,Cparties ahead of the Senedd Election
OL,6,FThis year there are some major changes
OL,7,Fcoming in, including new constituency
OL,8,Fboundaries. Wales is now divided into
OL,9,F16 constituencies and six Senedd
OL,10,FMembers will be elected in each one -
OL,11,Ftotalling 96 MSs overall.
OL,13,FPolitical parties can put forward up
OL,14,Fto eight candidates for each
OL,15,Fconstituency. You can find out your
OL,16,Fconstituency here.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
