OL,3,CThe main pledges from Wales' smaller
OL,4,Cparties ahead of the Senedd Election
OL,6,FWhile the major parties have fielded
OL,7,Fcandidates to every constituency, this
OL,8,Fis not the case for the smaller
OL,9,Fparties or independents. Here is a
OL,10,Fbreak down of the main Senedd Election
OL,11,Fpledges for each of Wales' smaller
OL,12,Fparties.
OL,14,FThe Heritage Party
OL,16,FThe Heritage Party is Wales' only
OL,17,Fsmaller party standing in each of
OL,18,FWales' 16 consistencies. They have
OL,19,Ffielded one candidate to each area
OL,20,Fapart from Afan Ogwr Rhondda, where
OL,21,Ftwo will be standing.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776625869
OL,3,CThe main pledges from Wales' smaller
OL,4,Cparties ahead of the Senedd Election
OL,6,FThe party says their policies are
OL,7,Fbased on "defending their culture and
OL,8,Fheritage". Their full manifesto can be
OL,9,Ffound here.
OL,11,FPolicies for the Senedd Election
OL,12,Finclude scrapping the comprehensive
OL,13,Fsexuality education, ending
OL,14,Fimmigration and the use of HMO's
OL,15,F(houses of multiple occupancy).
OL,17,FThey say they are against net zero
OL,18,Ftargets and the continuation of the
OL,19,F20mph speed limit policy. They also
OL,20,Fsay they would scrap the Senedd if
OL,21,Felected.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776625869
OL,3,CThe main pledges from Wales' smaller
OL,4,Cparties ahead of the Senedd Election
OL,6,FThere will be six candidates for Gwlad
OL,7,Fstanding for election across six
OL,8,Fconstituencies.
OL,10,FThe Gwlad party says they are
OL,11,F"eventually for independence for
OL,12,FWales". Their full manifesto can be
OL,13,Ffound here.
OL,15,FSome of their key policies include
OL,16,Fcutting the higher rate of income tax
OL,17,Fand expanding Welsh-medium primary and
OL,18,Fsecondary education. The party
OL,19,Fmanifesto says that student funding at
OL,20,Funiversity level education would be
OL,21,Flimited to those studying in Wales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
