FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776625869
OL,3,CThe main pledges from Wales' smaller
OL,4,Cparties ahead of the Senedd Election
OL,6,FAs for health, they say their first
OL,7,Fpriority would be to enhance primary
OL,8,Fcare provision to reduce pressure on
OL,9,Fsecondary care. In this area they
OL,10,Fwould look at alternative business
OL,11,Fmodels such as salaried services for
OL,12,FGPs and dentists.
OL,14,FOpen PartyJThere will be five
OL,15,Fcandidates standing for the Open Party
OL,16,Facross three constituencies.
OL,18,FThe party says their priority is to
OL,19,F"make politics available to the
OL,20,Fpublic" and for their "mandate to be
OL,21,Faccountable to the people".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
