PN,46407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776625869
OL,3,CThe main pledges from Wales' smaller
OL,4,Cparties ahead of the Senedd Election
OL,6,FRather than have a dedicated party
OL,7,Fmanifesto, each candidate puts forward
OL,8,Ftheir individual manifestos. The Open
OL,9,FParty says this makes candidates
OL,10,F"independent and free of any party
OL,11,Fagenda". Candidates are also chosen by
OL,12,Fthe public in the area they wish to
OL,13,Frepresent. Details of their principles
OL,14,Fcan be found here.
OL,16,FPropel are fielding four candidates
OL,17,Ffor the Senedd Election across two
OL,18,Fconstituencies.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
