PN,46410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776625869
OL,3,CThe main pledges from Wales' smaller
OL,4,Cparties ahead of the Senedd Election
OL,6,FSome of their key pledges include a
OL,7,Fmass council homes building campaign
OL,8,Fas well as strengthening rent
OL,9,Fcontrols. They would also look to
OL,10,Fnationalise energy companies in Wales
OL,11,Fand oppose the privatisation of public
OL,12,Fservices such as the NHS.
OL,14,FOn education, they would scrap
OL,15,Funiversity tuition fees, employ extra
OL,16,Fteachers and limit class sizes to 20
OL,17,Fpupils. Their full manifesto can be
OL,18,Ffound here.
OL,20,FWelsh Communist Party
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
