CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776625869
OL,3,CThe main pledges from Wales' smaller
OL,4,Cparties ahead of the Senedd Election
OL,6,FThere will be two candidates standing
OL,7,Ffor the Welsh Communist Party in two
OL,8,Fconstituencies.
OL,10,FSome of the party's key policies
OL,11,Finclude establishing a Welsh National
OL,12,FEconomic Development Authority to plan
OL,13,Finvestment and protect jobs.
OL,15,FThey say they would invest in
OL,16,Frenewable energy and bring energy rail
OL,17,Fand bus services into public
OL,18,Fownership. They would also take the
OL,19,FCrown Estate into public ownership.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
