CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776625869
OL,3,CThe main pledges from Wales' smaller
OL,4,Cparties ahead of the Senedd Election
OL,6,FThey say they oppose privatisation of
OL,7,Fany part of the NHS and would create a
OL,8,FNational Care Service. Their full
OL,9,Fmanifesto can be found here.
OL,11,FParties standing in a single
OL,12,Fconstituency
OL,14,FIndependent candidates
OL,16,FThere are also 30 independent
OL,17,Fcandidates standing in the Senedd
OL,18,FElection across 14 constituencies.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/13
